summaries.short: Season premiere. Magda and Teddy’s union has made Relu a hot commodity at the couple’s extravagant wedding festivities.
summaries.full: Season premiere. While Relu and Gina’s marriage has fallen apart, Magda and Teddy’s union has shaken up the pecking order within the Captain’s gang, making Relu a hot commodity at the couple’s extravagant wedding festivities. But when the newlyweds take off for their honeymoon, unexpected consequences loom.

summaries.short: The Captain and Relu agree to work together to stay one step ahead of the police and seek justice on their own terms.
summaries.full: With both of their families reeling after the devastating accident, the Captain and Relu agree to work together to stay one step ahead of the police and seek justice on their own terms. Meanwhile, Toma pays a visit to a dirty government agent, Sabin barters for his freedom, and a familiar face returns.

summaries.short: Season finale. After striking a deal with Toma, Relu makes arrangements to keep his family safe and cut ties with the Captain.
summaries.full: Season finale. After striking a deal with Toma, Relu makes arrangements to send his family to the countryside and cut ties with the Captain for good – but a surprise announcement from Magda and Teddy puts a wrench in his plans.

summaries.short: Relu uses unorthodox methods to extract a vital piece of information from Geamanu’ that brings him closer to avenging his daughter.
summaries.full: Relu uses unorthodox methods to extract a vital piece of information from Geamanu’ that brings him closer to avenging his daughter. A distraught Teddy gets involved in Relu’s revenge, bringing him deeper into the fold of the violent underground world than ever before. After a humiliating incident at a hotel, a crooked cop starts asking questions about the Captain’s enterprise.

summaries.short: Relu must return the stolen cash and produce the thief--or his wife and children will pay the price.
summaries.full: Puiu’s stunt lands him on the Captain’s blacklist, leaving Relu with a near-impossible task: return the stolen cash and produce the thief, or his wife and children will pay the price. With Nico’s help, Relu plots a dangerous heist to settle the score with the Captain.

Gina, now divorced, struggles to control her misbehaving son while her boss, Sebastian, takes a special interest in her. Teddy and Magda drift further apart.

summaries.full: In the wake of a botched job, the Captain looks for a scapegoat, and Relu attempts to retire from crime. Back at home, Gina considers giving Relu a second chance after he takes charge during a disciplinary meeting at Chuckie’s school. Puiu pulls a disappearing act that threatens the safety of the entire Oncescu family.
